casebody.data:
Thursday, March 7, 1996

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-2622. ALLTEL Ohio, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 94-1695-TP-ACE. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective March 6,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
